nya's Wins:**\n   - Wins with Rock: 9\n   - Wins with Scissors: 3\n   - Wins with Paper: 7\n   - Total Wins = \\( 9 + 3 + 7 = 19 \\)\n\n### Conclusion:\nAnya could win a total of \\( \\boxed{19} \\) games."}
