e\n\n        # Iterate over each character in the word\n        for char in word:\n            # If the character is not in the string or has been used up, the word is not formable\n            if char not in remaining_chars or remaining_chars[char] <= 0:\n                is_formable = False\n                break\n            # Otherwise, decrement the count of the character\n            else:\n                remaining_chars[char] -= 1\n\n        # If the word is formable, increment the counter\n        if is_formable:\n            formable_word_count += 1\n\n    # Return the count of formable words\n    return formable_word_count\n```"}
